<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>500 - 服务器错误</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/static/styles.css">
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f093fb 0%, #f5576c 100%);
        }
        .error-container {
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .error-card {
            background: white;
            padding: 60px 40px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
            max-width: 600px;
        }
        .error-code {
            font-size: 120px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #e67e22;
            margin: 0;
            line-height: 1;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5576c, #e67e22);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
        }
        .error-title {
            font-size: 32px;
            color: #2c3e50;
            margin: 20px 0 10px;
        }
        .error-description {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #7f8c8d;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .error-tips {
            background: #fff3cd;
            border-left: 4px solid #f5576c;
            padding: 15px 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: left;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        .error-tips h4 {
            margin: 0 0 10px 0;
            color: #856404;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .error-tips ul {
            margin: 0;
            padding-left: 20px;
            color: #856404;
        }
        .error-tips li {
            margin: 5px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .error-actions {
            display: flex;
            gap: 15px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        .error-link {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            background: #f5576c;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        .error-link:hover {
            background: #e74c3c;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(245, 87, 108, 0.4);
        }
        .error-link.secondary {
            background: #95a5a6;
        }
        .error-link.secondary:hover {
            background: #7f8c8d;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(149, 165, 166, 0.4);
        }
        .error-illustration {
            width: 200px;
            height: 200px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="error-container">
        <div class="error-card">
            <svg class="error-illustration" viewBox="0 0 200 200" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                <circle cx="100" cy="100" r="80" fill="#ecf0f1"/>
                <path d="M60 120 Q100 140 140 120" stroke="#f5576c" stroke-width="4" fill="none"/>
                <circle cx="75" cy="85" r="8" fill="#f5576c"/>
                <circle cx="125" cy="85" r="8" fill="#f5576c"/>
                <line x1="65" y1="80" x2="80" y2="70" stroke="#f5576c" stroke-width="4"/>
                <line x1="120" y1="70" x2="135" y2="80" stroke="#f5576c" stroke-width="4"/>
            </svg>

            <h1 class="error-code">500</h1>
            <h2 class="error-title">服务器内部错误</h2>
            <p class="error-description">
                抱歉，服务器遇到了一个意外错误，无法完成您的请求。<br>
                我们的技术团队已经收到通知，正在紧急处理。
            </p>

            <div class="error-tips">
                <h4>您可以尝试：</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li>刷新页面重试</li>
                    <li>稍后再次访问</li>
                    <li>清除浏览器缓存后重试</li>
                    <li>如果问题持续存在，请联系管理员</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="error-actions">
                <a href="javascript:location.reload()" class="error-link">刷新页面</a>
                <a href="/" class="error-link secondary">返回首页</a>
                <a href="/users.html" class="error-link secondary">用户管理</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
